cabal-version: 3.0
name: socket-effectful
version: 0.1.0.0
synopsis:
  Adaptation of the socket library for the effectful ecosystem.

description:
  Adaptation of the @<https://hackage.haskell.org/package/socket socket>@ library for the @<https://hackage.haskell.org/package/effectful effectful>@ ecosystem.

homepage: https://github.com/Cajunvoodoo/socket-effectful#readme
bug-reports: https://github.com/Cajunvoodoo/socket-effectful/issues
license: BSD-3-Clause
license-file: LICENSE
author: Cajunvoodoo
maintainer: 27892784+Cajunvoodoo@users.noreply.github.com
